      "text": "nefi eekſch teem Stiprumeem/ \nun palikke us weenu Kalnu eekſch\nSiwas Tukfneses. Un Sauls\nmekleja to allachin/ bet Deews\nne dewe to winna Rohkâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Dahwids redſeja/\nka Sauls bija iſgahjts winna\nDſhwibu mekleht. Tad bija\nDahwids eekſch Siwas Tukfne-\nfes/ Sillâ."
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs Jonatans/\nSaula Dehls/ un gahje pee Dah-\nwida Sillâ/ un ſiprinaja win-\nna Rohku eekſch Deewa."
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un fazzija uſ to: Ne bih-\nſtees/ jo manna Tehwa Saula\nRohka tew ne atraddihs/ un tu\ntapti par Kehniſu pahr Iſraêlu/\ntad buhfchu es tas tuwakajs pee\ntewis/ un to paſchu mans Tehws\nSauls arri gann finna."
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee abbt darrija weenu\nDerribu preeſch ta KUNGA/\nun Dahwids palikke tai Sillâ/\nbet Jonatans gahje us Mahju."
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nogahje tee Siwiteri\npee Santa uhs Gibeju/ un faz-\nzija: Neggi Dahwids turrahs\nfleppeni pee mums Sillâ eekſch\nteem Stiprumeem/ us to Pakal-\nnu Akilu/ kas Tuksneſei pa lab-\nbo Rohku?"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Nu tad/ Kehniſch/ nahz\ntuhdalin pehz wiſſu tawu Sirđs\nPrahti/ jo mumis peenahk win-\nnu ta Kehnika Rohkâ nodcht."
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Sauls: Sweh-\ntiti eſat juhs tam KUNGAM/\nka juhs pahr man eſat apscheh-\nlojschee."
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eita jelle/ darrajt to weh-\nun nemmeet wehra/ un iſluhke\njeet winna Weetu/ kur wiſſc\nturrahs/ kas winnu tur redſej\nirr/ jo man irr fazzihts/ ka ta\nfohti gudrs irr."
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tapehz peeraugajt un is-\nlubkojeet wiſſas Weetas/ ku\nwinna Pehdas buhs/ tad nahze-\natkat pee man ar ihſtaim Weh-\nſtim/ tad eefchu es ar jums lihd-\nUn ja wiſſch tchai Seininê buhs\ntad dſihſchohs es winnam pat-\nkak starp wiſſeem tuhkſtoscheen\neekſch Iuhda."
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad zehlehs tee/ un no-\ngahje us Siwu Saulam papreek-\nschu: Bet Dahwids un win-\nWihti turrejahs eekſch Maona\nTukfneses Klatjuma/ pa labba-\nRohkas tahs Tukfnibas."
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sauls ar faweem\nWihtreem gahje winnu metleht\ntad tappe Dahwidam Wehſt-\ndohta. Tad nogahje tas us to lee-\nsu Akmini/ un palikke eekſch Ma-\nona Tukfnibas. Kad nu Saul-\nto dsirdeja/ dsinnahs wiſſch Dah-\nwidam pakkat eekſch Maona\nTukfneses."
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sauls gahje fcha-\nKalna Puſſê/ un Dahwids ar fa-\nweem Wihtreim winna Kaln-\nPuſſê: Tad steidſehs Dahwid-\npreeſch Saula behgt/ bet Saul-\nar faweem Wihtreem nahze ap-\nkaht Dahwidu/ un apkahrt win-\nna Wthreem/ tohs faguhſtiht."
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet weens Wehſtneſi-\nnahze vee Saula/ tazzidains\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
